data.description:
Lovely Colonial in the center of town.
Updated 3 Bedroom and 2 Bath home with great curb appeal. Large open foyer with gleaming hardwood floors throughout the first and second floor:  Wood burning fireplace, Spacious Eat-in-kitchen with Center Island. 3 Lovely bedrooms. Full bath with Marble shower stall.  Finished Walk-out basement with a full bath. Walkup Attic space for future expansion. For outdoor entertaining, the home boasts a lovely fenced backyard. Paver patio, and  fire pit. Detached garage. Newer timberline roof, updated utilities - 2 Zone A/C, Tankless continuous Hot water heater. Outdoor Lighting, Spacious Kitchen with slider leading to a 2 tiered deck. The home is immaculate and a pleasure to show. The home is centrally located and within walking distance of all the amenities in town: Restaurants, shopping and entertaining.
